Content: **Deep Learning Advanced Course Syllabus**

**Course Overview**

This 100-hour course is designed for advanced students interested in deep learning. The course will cover the core concepts, advanced applications, and practical aspects of deep learning. Students will gain hands-on experience with deep learning frameworks and tools, and apply their knowledge to real-world projects.

**Course Outline**

The course is divided into 24 modules, each lasting 60 minutes. The modules are organized into four sections: Foundations, Core Concepts, Advanced Applications, and Capstone.

